## Stack Description

- Build tool: Maven
- Language: Java 26
- Framework: Spring Boot 4.0.3
- API style: REST (Spring Web MVC)
- Persistence: Spring Data JPA
- Database (local/dev): H2
- API docs: Springdoc OpenAPI UI (`springdoc-openapi-starter-webmvc-ui`)
- Dev tooling: Spring Boot DevTools
- Testing: Spring Boot Web MVC Test starter

## Dependency Baseline (from `pom.xml`)

- `org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-h2console`
- `org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-data-jpa`
- `org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-webmvc`
- `org.springdoc:springdoc-openapi-starter-webmvc-ui`
- `org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-devtools` (runtime, optional)
- `com.h2database:h2` (runtime)
- `org.springframework.boot:spring-boot-starter-webmvc-test` (test)

## Usage Rules

- Treat this file as the single source of truth for stack information.
- When dependencies or framework/runtime versions change, update this file first.
- Other rules must reference this file instead of duplicating stack/version details.
